title: [Air Tower, Library]
description: Two lines of bookcases are formless lumps in the shadowy darkness, the aisle between them ending in a window overlooking a courtyard below.  The bookcases are stuffed with books, tomes, scrolls, and pamphlets in various stages of disrepair.

Two lines of bookcases march the length of the room, the aisle between them ending in a window overlooking a courtyard below.  The bookcases are stuffed with books, tomes, scrolls, and pamphlets in various stages of disrepair, and motes of dust hang listlessly in the air.
